{"tid":162101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【老鼠之城】澳洲雪梨老鼠多過人     體型好似貓咁大","createTime":"2017-03-19T04:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T17:38:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff3afab9cb900bbe1280b7ef70a6861a13c9792","tid":162101,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170319/large/1489864297_7b6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170319%2Flarge%2F1489864297_7b6e.jpg&h=aef0d5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 【新增影片】<br />\n澳洲雪梨鼠患嚴重，老鼠數量比人口更多，而且體型有貓般大，市議會收到的相關投訴大增75%，令他們頭痛不已。<br />\n<br />\n雪梨除了橫街窄巷有老鼠，甚至旅遊熱點如海德公園和環形碼頭都現鼠蹤。由於老鼠帶有病菌，會引發肝臟疾病和傳播沙門氏菌，因此鼠患亦帶來衛生問題。<br />\n<br />\n市議會獨立議員維多卡斯(Angela Vithoulkas)說，雪梨以前也有老鼠，但沒有現在那麼多，她希望所有新建築均能採取一些新的滅鼠方法。<br />\n<br />\n市議會發言人說，由於近日拆樓和建樓項目增多，令老鼠急速繁殖，市議會會定期進行諸如放老鼠藥等滅鼠行動。當地一位滅鼠專家說，老鼠數量可以控制，但要將之完全滅絕是不太可能。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲新快網"},{"pid":"608add770b2ce024274367c530d01ff33d99d8ec","tid":162101,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:43:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d080e630b3aa3148800bed30e962f9cfd755f14a","tid":162101,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:46:28.000Z","msg":"全民養貓"},{"pid":"26eee15815561e262ec248a648159138af13c95a","tid":162101,"uid":49359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:47:20.000Z","msg":"但係澳洲d貓又成隻狗大"},{"pid":"f205b9b73ec7999a483229c34ab20dd00fde19fe","tid":162101,"uid":37505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係澳洲d貓又成隻狗大</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁啲狗會唔會老虎咁大隻"},{"pid":"77bd6bddaf2ac1018b20e418a13c363b64e2f81c","tid":162101,"uid":64969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全民養貓</blockquote><br />\n貓係澳洲冇天敵,依家澳野貓已經令好多動物絕種/瀕危,澳洲每年都會毒殺百萬隻貓,但都追唔上貓既繁殖速度"},{"pid":"1f06954f3c2dc650cf29094758f4890212c3e4ef","tid":162101,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全民養貓</blockquote><br />\n貓係澳洲冇天敵,依家澳野貓已經令好多動物絕種/瀕危,澳洲每年都會毒殺百萬隻貓,但都追唔上貓既繁殖速度</blockquote><br />\n殺完貓到老鼠瘋狂繁殖，要點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a942504b944868207844748dda4d825590097696","tid":162101,"uid":38970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"悉尼老鼠"},{"pid":"9f7eecc973049cf9fc842b0e00b241c339b92840","tid":162101,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>悉尼老鼠</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303651c81070eb2c297c9455bf17bc69f53727e1","tid":162101,"uid":36483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>悉尼老鼠</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1964881e48c4e796fe2b007e28547aec38c05f9","tid":162101,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"鼠患"},{"pid":"e240a81dcfbd7fff9c20013de27bc7a87a0e2bc3","tid":162101,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/81/1308439245.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20110619160731\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette1.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F81%2F1308439245.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D